snippet.textDisplay:
This is serene. Good to see that Nabeel is doing wonders with his voice after winning Sur Kshetra. The musical arrangement, the lyrics, the composition and basically every aspect of this song has got me hooked with the very first note. Also, I use to have this biased perceptions that only Indians are blessed with melodious classical flautist but I have been proved drastically wrong. Pakistani flautists are at par with the Indian counterparts. Desperately waiting to listen to more pak coke studio songs.
Lots of love and respect from India :)
